text: Scott from google just pinged me, says they think they know what was up with that ID issue that he was having, and has jose looking into it. Has another issue, that i think I know what is going on, I am going to look into it a little bit and see if i can give him more info. It has to do with the call for the door close on changing of the preset. It sounds like its failing on them. Im not sure why it would be. Im going to look and see if there is anything obvious / remind myself how that worked exactly so i can either fix it or give them a direction to look.

turned out there wasnt really an issue, the hardware for the lights was offline causing the connection timeouts. Educated scott a little more on how timeouts are set in the code. He said the timeout seems too good them.
